      <title>巴西廉价咖啡现在比高档阿拉比卡咖啡更贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/brazil-s-cheap-coffee-is-now-costlier-than-fancy-arabica-beans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上最便宜的咖啡品种正面临着严重的短缺，其咖啡豆的价格已经比星巴克公司青睐的高档咖啡豆还要贵，至少在主要种植区巴西是这样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/brazil-s-cheap-coffee-is-now-costlier-than-fancy-arabica-beans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:29:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“健康饮食风潮”推动豆芽销量翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/sprouts-shares-double-as-healthy-eating-wave-powers-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sprouts Farmers Market Inc. 今年的股价已经增长了一倍多，Evercore ISI 认为，随着这家天然和有机食品零售商利用富裕购物者对健康饮食的关注获利，其股价还将持续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/sprouts-shares-double-as-healthy-eating-wave-powers-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:19:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西石油首席财务官认为下一个商业计划中的支出“切合实际”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/petrobras-cfo-sees-realistic-spending-in-next-business-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席财务官费尔南多·梅尔加雷霍 (Fernando Melgarejo) 在视频采访中表示，巴西石油公司的下一个五年商业计划将具有切合实际的投资水平，并且可能包括增加公司可以承担的债务数额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/petrobras-cfo-sees-realistic-spending-in-next-business-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
